{
  "stem": "23599.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Five minutes00 it was very close, like in the-- in the center.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was close.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I walked because it was close.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But some walked and some didn't, depending how far they were away.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was mixed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] It was a mixed class.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we had-- in town, we had the Maccabi, a group where-- and there was a man that was brought in even from Vienna.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he was in-- he was looked after there-- [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] he-- how do you say-- [PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] I forgot now the name-- how you say it-- he looked after the activities-- after activities and gymnastic, and things like that.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Gymnastic.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We liked gymnastic.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, later, I mean there was all later, there was skiing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then I had some older cousins and they took me along, always.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we had lessons twice a week where we went for gymnastic, twice a week.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was a place where we had all kinds of-- [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] well, we had quite a few where we could go and exercise, different exercises.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then there was the time we had the men in the town who-- who-- who-- he was a builder.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He had a big company, and he helped us to build a chalet in the mountains.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So the students, the older students, they would go there in summer time and at the holiday, and they would even stay there, and helped to build the building to the house.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's where the Beskids, part of the Tatra.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] These where the Beskids, so-called.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What do you mean by special?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I was very close with my father.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
